---
import ZoneLayout from '../../layouts/ZoneLayout.astro'
import SceneTownSquare from '../../components/scenes/SceneTownSquare.astro'
---

<ZoneLayout zone="project-track" title="Tracks — spicyninja.org">
  <SceneTownSquare slot="scene" />

  <div style="padding: 12vh 3.5rem 6rem; max-width: 960px;">
    <p class="eyebrow">pedagogy system</p>
    <h1 class="hero-heading" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">The Three Tracks</h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body); font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--text-secondary);
              max-width:600px; line-height:1.85; margin-bottom:4rem;">
      Three distinct ways through the same material. Each makes different assumptions
      about what you want and what you already know.
    </p>

    <div style="display:grid; gap:1px; background:var(--border);">

      <a href="/project-track"
         style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:3px 1fr; background:var(--bg-card);
                text-decoration:none; transition:background 0.2s ease;"
         onmouseover="this.style.background='var(--bg-raised)'"
         onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--bg-card)'">
        <div style="background:var(--cinnabar);" />
        <div style="padding:2rem 2.5rem;">
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.52rem; letter-spacing:0.28em;
                     text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--cinnabar); margin-bottom:0.6rem;">Track 01</p>
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display); font-weight:400; font-size:2rem;
                      color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.8rem; line-height:1;">Project Track</h2>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-body); color:var(--text-secondary); font-size:0.95rem;
                     line-height:1.75; max-width:560px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;">
            The original edifying syllabus. Twenty-two works across five modules, each chosen
            because it teaches something irreplaceable and load-bearing for making <em>Jus Pulsus</em>.
            Sequence matters. Everything here serves a specific compositional need.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:2rem; font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.58rem;
                       letter-spacing:0.15em; color:var(--text-ghost);">
            <span>22 works</span><span>5 modules</span><span>4-layer methodology</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/montessori"
         style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:3px 1fr; background:var(--bg-card);
                text-decoration:none; transition:background 0.2s ease;"
         onmouseover="this.style.background='var(--bg-raised)'"
         onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--bg-card)'">
        <div style="background:#c8922a;" />
        <div style="padding:2rem 2.5rem;">
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.52rem; letter-spacing:0.28em;
                     text-transform:uppercase; color:#c8922a; margin-bottom:0.6rem;">Track 02</p>
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display); font-weight:400; font-size:2rem;
                      color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.8rem; line-height:1;">Montessori Experience Track</h2>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-body); color:var(--text-secondary); font-size:0.95rem;
                     line-height:1.75; max-width:560px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;">
            An infinitely branching knowledge tree. Nodes unlock nodes. Follow curiosity rather
            than a prescribed sequence. Connected to the project but doesn't require it.
            Bespoke Journey Courses live inside this track.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:2rem; font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.58rem;
                       letter-spacing:0.15em; color:var(--text-ghost);">
            <span>branching tree</span><span>self-directed</span><span>Björk Bodysuit inaugural journey</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/fundamentals"
         style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:3px 1fr; background:var(--bg-card);
                text-decoration:none; transition:background 0.2s ease;"
         onmouseover="this.style.background='var(--bg-raised)'"
         onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--bg-card)'">
        <div style="background:#6b3fa0;" />
        <div style="padding:2rem 2.5rem;">
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.52rem; letter-spacing:0.28em;
                     text-transform:uppercase; color:#6b3fa0; margin-bottom:0.6rem;">Track 03</p>
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display); font-weight:400; font-size:2rem;
                      color:var(--text-primary); margin-bottom:0.8rem; line-height:1;">Fundamentals</h2>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-body); color:var(--text-secondary); font-size:0.95rem;
                     line-height:1.75; max-width:560px; margin-bottom:1.2rem;">
            Five branches of compositional technique: Bach math, Markov chains, music theory,
            composition, character development. General courses illustrated with Sonic Pi,
            grounded in tradition, cross-referenced to the project in development.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:2rem; font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.58rem;
                       letter-spacing:0.15em; color:var(--text-ghost);">
            <span>5 branches</span><span>Sonic Pi throughout</span><span>project callouts</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</ZoneLayout>
